Then and Now 1980: Sony Walkman with Cassette (Then: $169.00 / Now: $19.95), Ross Harris (Then: Movie star of &quot;Airplane!&quot; / Now: Video star of &quot;Sad Caper&quot; by Hootie and the Blowfish) and The Big Gulp (Then: 32 oz. / Now: 64 oz.)

