* “Freight Train Boogie” - The Delmore Brothers
* &quot;Knocking Down Casey Jones&quot; – Wilmer Watts
* &quot;What&#x27;s Next to the Moon&quot; – AC/DC
* “Casey Jones—the Union Scab” – Joe Hill
